Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.94,0:27:39.43,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}目を覚ましたとき いつもの癖で「おはよう」
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.94,0:27:39.43,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}酣夢初醒 一如往常問早安
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.22,0:27:52.79,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}あと何度 同じ泣きそうな顔させるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.22,0:27:52.79,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}曾經幾回 為君而面露哀傷
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.09,0:28:06.67,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}その運命は まるで蛍火のように見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.09,0:28:06.67,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}命若螢火 過眼雲煙轉瞬逝
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.64,0:28:21.27,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}風を泳ぐように 心を揺らすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.64,0:28:21.27,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}心亂情惘 如若遊弋狂風中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.72,0:28:34.79,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}何度も 何度も 問いかけても
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.72,0:28:34.79,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}曾幾回 曾幾回 尋蹤覓跡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.98,0:28:42.06,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}鏡に写る日々は 答えくれない
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.98,0:28:42.06,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}杳然無信 鏡中倒影無回音
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.42,0:28:51.65,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}いつかは 消えた未来もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.42,0:28:51.65,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}斷緣再續 終將有時
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.38,0:28:58.13,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}信じたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.38,0:28:58.13,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}心誠則明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教室？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.64,0:00:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是我認識的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的學生證
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.52,0:01:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說那是一個下雨天的放學後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.79,0:01:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一名女教師從樓梯拐角掉下去摔死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時的校長對待學校 就像對待自己的孩子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是慘劇接二連三
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在某一天發生了兇殺案之後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便決定廢校了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說在那之後校長心疾不愈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在學校關閉的當天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:02:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他從學校的屋頂上跳樓自殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在所就讀的這個如月學園
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是建在那被詛咒的天神小學的遺址之上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.33,0:02:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說摔死的那個老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並沒有意識到自己已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像在這種雨天的放學之後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她依舊徘徊在漆黑的校園裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 差不多就是這個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧 哲志
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個 我們差不多該撤了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎同學 繼續講嘛 繼續繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繭你膽子也很小的 還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森繁 為什麼要說「也」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別鬧 別鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那樣子會被直美討厭的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 世以子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎 快繼續講吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個老師出現的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學校肯定會停電 變得一片漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後在「砰砰」的敲門聲之後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,門會「吱~」的一下被拉開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張慘白的臉探向教室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還會問「還有人留在這嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才有人敲門了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯…錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎 玩笑開太過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 這黑的都看不到蠟燭放哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要有光 燈的開關呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.19,0:03:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開關在門邊上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有人留在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結衣老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲志…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你往哪抓呢？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們打算待到幾點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是讓你們處理完文化祭的後事之後就回去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說是給你帶傘來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼 哲志的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在上初中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面 我是持田由香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥一直承蒙各位照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼都不知道哲志你還有個這麼可愛的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 我沒提到過麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最喜歡哥哥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 你和岸沼見過面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣放鬆真的沒問題嗎 有這麼一個強大對手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢 世以子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後能再做一件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸福的幸子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是網上流傳的咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說一起做這個的人就會永不分離
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都會是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個姐姐怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要轉學了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的文化祭也是她最後一次和我們在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴走了讓人感到很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是搬家 其實也沒太遠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以寒假時候我們一定會來玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要不要當個帶隊老師跟過去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候我會準備好新的鬼故事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是喜歡這玩意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一直都是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能遇上大家真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會忘記大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要哭到什麼時候去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 笑一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家圍著這個幸子人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後在心中默念「拜託了 幸子小姐」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要念9遍喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念錯沒事 但千萬別改口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說念的次數和認輸對不上的話就會失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失敗的話會怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得好緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都要在心中默念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「拜託了 幸子小姐」9遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預備 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都念好9遍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那下來把手伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便挑一個幸子人偶的一部分捏住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 用手捏緊之後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起把它扯掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預備 拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家把自己的紙片夾在學生證或者錢包裡帶著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個算是護符嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說只要帶著這個紙片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就能一直作為朋友連在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來就是這樣的一個咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 這個不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對不會弄丟的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎同學 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會把它當作寶貝帶著的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一定會再見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約好了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 大家差不多就準備回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快躲桌子底下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼 在哪給扭了一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然感覺是掉下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子 世以子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 直美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到午休時間了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是問「怎麼了」的時候啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不記得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化祭結束收拾完教室之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在教室玩了個咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 打不開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手機也沒信號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想這裡會不會是個靈異點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你又不是班長 就別嚇人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我們為什麼會在那種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道我們被綁架了什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被捲入了什麼事件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開個玩笑啦 不會有那種事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子 你剛聽見什麼聲音了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 我什麼都沒聽見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是微妙的很安靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之我們趕快從這出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 直美 你腳怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 稍微崴了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能走的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那教室裡的桌椅你不覺得有點小嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡會不會是小學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像只有我們兩個在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和直美的二人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等..等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都這樣了還鬧什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們趕緊從這裡出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那麼著急啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想再和直美單獨待一會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 直美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帶了治屁股的藥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能等出去了再說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般的軟膏我是有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去去就來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快自重一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡也打不開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下去就是一樓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該有緊急出口的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就能出去了 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現出口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好小的鞋子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像世以子說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡應該是小學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小學嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家大概肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你弟弟悠他們也是小學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是長身體的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光給他們做飯就快累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為世以子的爸爸回家很晚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 爸爸努力工作的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是家庭主婦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能照顧那幫弟弟的也就我和爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.03,0:16:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真偉大 只是個高中生就當媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得這話好微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了我們趕快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且直美你也得早點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你媽一個人在家等著你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會在擔心我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心著呢 擔心著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持田同學肯定也在擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 搞不好他就在外面等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎麼會扯到這個話題上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喊 一 二 一起開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找個地方稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 肯定能出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 完美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有什麼東西能冷敷一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫了大忙了 世以子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 直美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後你也會跟我在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我和世以子不管發生了什麼 都會是朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子你昨晚也問了這個問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:17:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一直在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想把那個重要的紙片給弄丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得應該在廁所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 咱一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直美就好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來了就一起去找出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在一起…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體…動不了 也發不出聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假大家一起去遠足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再痛苦一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我！世以子！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸 你是來接我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直美？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直美！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭髮？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪 小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到這邊來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到這…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直美！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直美 沒事吧 直美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.04,0:22:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼現在才來？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是說馬上回來嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差點就被幹掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還說什麼一直在一起啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.55,0:22:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我一個人丟在一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害我遇到了這種危險的事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧你還能說出這種話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.47,0:22:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你算什麼啊 一天到晚都在傻笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想讓直美好好休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭！ 我才不想被直美你說成這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被直美這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.77,0:22:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被直美討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.12,0:22:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我沒陪在他身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得趕快跟直美道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.17,0:23:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.42,0:23:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼會對世以子說出那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去和世以子道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.61,0:23:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才給世以子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.68,0:24:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子 你在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽我說 剛才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.44,0:24:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在裡面嗎 世以子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.69,0:24:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.86,0:24:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以…子？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.73,0:24:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 為什麼要這樣啊 世以子！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.12,0:24:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子 你還活著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.90,0:24:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…不…起...對…不…起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.66,0:24:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.86,0:24:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該道歉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.33,0:24:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.19,0:24:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.22,0:24:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.07,0:25:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 對了 把繩子… 把繩子解開
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.26,0:25:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不行 這樣只會勒的更緊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.83,0:25:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.67,0:25:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼能墊腳的東西的話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.37,0:25:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿那個墊腳
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.24,0:25:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.12,0:25:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼為什麼為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.36,0:25:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要上吊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.47,0:26:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才你不是還在笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.63,0:26:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說好一起回去的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.37,0:26:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 不要這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.80,0:26:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別丟下我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.02,0:26:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回一聲啊 世以子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.32,0:26:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾個小時前還在教室裡談笑風生的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.71,0:26:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吊死在了眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.72,0:26:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能有人接受這樣的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.25,0:26:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這裡一切都有可能發生
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.06,0:26:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.33,0:26:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那遭受詛咒的…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.30,0:26:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天神小學
